'''千禧公園'''（{{lang-en|'''Millennium Park'''}}）又稱'''千禧年公園'''，是位在美國伊利諾州[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[洛普區|洛普區]]的一座大型[[公園|公園]]。本公園是[[密西根湖|密西根湖]]湖畔重要的[[文化娛樂中心|文化娛樂中心]]，含蓋整個格蘭特公園西北邊{{convert|24.5|acre|m2}}的土地。該地區曾經被[[伊利諾中央鐵路|伊利諾中央鐵路]]（Illinois Central Railroad）當作停車場使用<ref>[http://tigger.uic.edu/depts/ahaa/imagebase/maclean/aerials1/05.JPEG This picture] {{Wayback|url=http://tigger.uic.edu/depts/ahaa/imagebase/maclean/aerials1/05.JPEG |date=20150402121653 }} shows Grant Park before Millennium Park (upper right) was built.</ref>。截至2009年，千禧公園是全芝加哥人氣第二高的旅遊景點，僅次於[[海军码头|海军码头]]（Navy's Pier）<ref name=crain>{{cite news|title=Crain's List: Chicago's Largest Tourist Attractions (Sightseeing): Ranked by 2009 attendance|date=March 22, 2010|page=21|publisher=[[Crain_Communications_Inc.|Crain Communications Inc.]]|work=Crain's Chicago Business}}</ref>。

==历史==
公園從1997年10月開始規劃，1998年10月開始建造，2004年7月16日啟用，但比計畫中的進度落後了4年。大約有30萬人參加為期3天的開幕音樂會。千禧公園啟用至今已經得到[[無障礙|無障礙]]與綠色設計等獎項<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.millenniumpark.org/newsandmedia/pdfs/4.1%20Millennium%20Park%20Awards.pdf |format=PDF |title=Chicago's New Millennium Park Wins Travel & Leisure Design Award For "Best Public Space", And The American Public Works Association "Project Of The Year" Award |accessdate=June 24, 2008 |date=April 12, 2005 |publisher=City of Chicago |author=Ryan, Karen |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080910132600/http://www.millenniumpark.org/newsandmedia/pdfs/4.1%20Millennium%20Park%20Awards.pdf |archivedate=2008-09-10 }}</ref>。本公園是屬於免費入場的性質<ref name=LFC>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9806EED71E3BF930A25754C0A9629C8B63|title=Letter From Chicago; A Prized Project, a Mayor and Persistent Criticism|accessdate=May 31, 2008|date=July 13, 2004|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|author=Kinzer, Stephen|archive-date=2009-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307053618/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9806EED71E3BF930A25754C0A9629C8B63|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

